metadata.name: Frozen Life I No. 3
metadata.description:
"Frozen Life I No. 3" is part of my project "Frozen Life". The project has started in 2008.

The images in this ongoing series were all made during whiteouts in the Black Forest, Germany.

Date of photograph: 2008

Location: Black Forest, Germany

A signed fine art print is provided to the first collector of this piece.
